channel.title: Intrepid - The Calling (Little Baby Remix)
channel.description:
Hey Guys! I got a replacement pair of headphones and I just made a remix of @IntrepidMusic 's ["The Calling"](https://itunes.apple.com/album/id1272311908?ls=1&app=itunes)
Sorry for those of you who already listened to it on [SoundCloud](https://www.soundcloud.com/littlebabu), I titled it incorrectly because when I was typing the name I was listening to an Austin Haga song, but here you go!
https://soundcloud.com/littlebabu/intrepid-the-calling
Thanks! -Little Baby
